Title: Time-Varying Coefficient Spatial Autoregressive Panel Data Model with Fixed Effects
Author-Name: Xuan Liang
Author-X-Name-First: Xuan
Author-X-Name-Last: Liang
Author-Email: xuan.liang@anu.edu.au
