Title: Spatial modelling of the two-party preferred vote in Australian federal elections: 2001-2016
Author-Name: Jeremy Forbes
Author-X-Name-First: Jeremy 
Author-X-Name-Last: Forbes
Author-Email: jeremyforbes1995@gmail.com
Author-Name: Dianne Cook
Author-X-Name-First: Dianne 
